  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个工业物联网场景下的收益优化流程。核心想法是把DeFi的收益聚合逻辑映射到工业边缘计算架构里——YieldVaultMultiAsset作为边缘节点，Aave V3 Pool作为PLC逻辑层，RSC模块负责实时决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "YieldVaultMultiAsset",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Aave V3 Pool",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "YieldOptimizerRsc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以User触发后，Vault作为边缘节点先去Aave拉取储备数据，对吗？然后RSC这个收益优化器在边缘侧做计算，而不是把原始数据传回云端？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Vault",
        "Aave V3 Pool",
        "YieldOptimizerRsc",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，RSC在边缘节点本地完成APY对比和再平衡决策，减少延迟。只有需要执行调仓时，才通过Callback Proxy通知Vault。这个Proxy也是部署在PLC逻辑层的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "YieldOptimizerRsc",
        "Callback Proxy",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "YieldVaultMultiAsset"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主要参与方画出来：User、Vault（标注为IoT工业边缘节点）、Aave V3 Pool（标注为IoT工业PLC逻辑）、RSC（同样是边缘节点）、还有Callback Proxy（PLC逻辑层）。顶部加个注释说明这是收益监控与再平衡流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "YieldVaultMultiAsset",
        "Aave V3 Pool",
